{"tid":1642010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新港城四期週末一事 陰謀論","createTime":"2019-10-09T14:06:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T14:13:22.000Z","uid":41873,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b2a41f7f5dd6de97bcfd9433a65e7c9f3871d29a","tid":1642010,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:06:21.000Z","msg":"本身<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">馬鞍山</span></span></strong>都係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">黃到七彩</span></span></span></strong>架啦<br />\n林鄭見有機會可以藉呢件事<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">影響下當區居民既週末生活 </span></span></strong><br />\n仲唔黎一個打蛇隨棍上<br />\n搞返你一個週末先<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">令到當區居民有聲音話影響到佢地既日常生活<br />\n從而再分化我地</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n明明今晚都係唱歌叫口號好地地 <br />\n做乜要無啦啦咁大陣象要一個週末唔開商場先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 陰謀論 <br />\n如有雷同 實屬巧合"},{"pid":"e49fc2f96a393940357224efd110e0e3c0d68b04","tid":1642010,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:06:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0234f625a39757cc77dd36fe005f5ca19ea3c969","tid":1642010,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:06:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9ca867e0202bf2941c50c51a147e4bb2e0662fd","tid":1642010,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:06:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"835ecc11863caf0eaf7936ca2b1b2b0f1937bb61","tid":1642010,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:07:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"279352b2b1bf1d7d679b32d7b06afab3f8e791df","tid":1642010,"uid